description: Make your next special event even more deliciously special by inviting this big yellow too-cool-for-school bus to come to your door and provide all your guests with the finest, most flavorful frozen treats in all of Fort Worth. SnowieBusDFW is bringing the family-friendly fun to everyone with their flashing and spinning carnival lights, speakers that are blasting your favorite tunes, and a flavor station filled with all your favorite fruity flavors, so that you can customize your own sweet creations. For a delightfully nice and icy time, SnowieBusDFW is an absolute must.
name: SnowieBus DFW
